DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-05-17T03:30:00&endDate=2026-05-17T06:40:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nELIZABETH LINE: Sunday 17 May\, until 0740\, no service between Paddington and Ealing Broadway. Please use Central line connections between Central London and Ealing Broadway. In addition the 2345 Saturday evening GWR Didcot Parkway to Paddington train terminates at Ealing Broadway and does not call at Burnham. The 0034 GWR Paddington to Reading train will not call at Burnham. For Burnham\, use connecting buses to/from Slough.
